# in JUST that cloned script to auto-accept (vendoring-0 invariant: only the runtime clone's
# working tree is edited, the upstream commit is untouched). GR-1's downloader has a real
# argparse `-y`, so this is RoboCasa-Kitchen-only.
log "[5/8] FIX 9: making download_kitchen_assets.py non-interactive (auto-accept ~5GB DL)..."
